:{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 102.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' The whole crew was watching me &mdash; it was pretty embarrassing...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Rescued from the ice?
::{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 103.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Oh, I forgot to tell you.
::{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 104.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Before all this, I was stuck in a huge block of ice drifting through space.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} The whole crew was watching you?
::{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 105.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Uh-huh! Like I was some kind of weird alien! I don't really blame them for being curious though &mdash; they had no idea where I came from.
::{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 106.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' You might not believe it, but before all this, I was stuck in a huge block of ice drifting through space.
:{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 107.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Himeko and Mr. Yang and... who was it again? Anyway, they figured out a way to melt the ice and saved me.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} How did you get frozen?
::{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 108.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Who knows? I don't remember anything before that.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Do you remember what happened before you were frozen?
::{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 109.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' I don't remember a thing.
:{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 110.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Who I am, where I'm from, my name... it's like everything was erased from my mind. "March 7th" was the day they found me, so it stuck.
:{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 111.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Ever since then, I've been hanging out on this train and following it to whatever destination it decides to stop at. I'm hoping that one day, I can find my past...
:{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 112.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Ugh, what am I talking about this for? Way to get everyone down, huh.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sorry.
::{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 113.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' It's fine. I was the one who brought it up.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...
:{{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 114 m.ogg}} {{A|VO chapter0 8 mar7th 114 f.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Cheer up, (Trailblazer)! It's not every day someone gets to ride on the Astral Express...
